Now, calculate `total_energy`.

Method:

For loop to accumulate

Return `monthly_target` together with `total_energy`

Complete User Flow

Complete Usage Flow:

User Login
↓ Set Monthly Goal
↓ Enter Daily Electricity Consumption
↓ System Records
↓ Calculate Monthly Electricity Consumption

New Features

1️⃣ Prevent Duplicate Records on the Same Day (Feature 1)

If there is already a record today → Update energy

If not → Add record

2️⃣ Input Validation + Error Messages (Feature 2)

Username is empty
energy is empty
energy is negative
target is empty
target is negative

Clear message will be returned for all errors.

Explanation of New Feature Logic

Feature 1: Prevent Duplicate Dates

New Logic:
for record in records:
    if record["date"] == today:
        record["energy"] = energy

Feature 2: Input Error Prompt

Input checking is now available for all APIs.
